- Move iTerm and Alfred settings on other hosts
- Update setup script to use Python
- Make sure that a few things are installed before running the script (brew basically)
- Separate things among platforms
- Install fish in the script by using brew
- Change the shell to fish in the setup script


You will need to add:
  /usr/local/bin/fish
  to /etc/shells.

  Then run:
    chsh -s /usr/local/bin/fish
    to make fish your default shell.
